=head1 NAME

unregistered_japanese_authors - try to find unregistered Japanese CPAN authors

=head1 SYNOPSIS

 > unregistered_japanese_authors

=head1 DESCRIPTION

You can use this to find Pause IDs whose real name looks like Japanese.

